      "text_preview": "Aranya Digital Services Ltd \u2014 Annual Report FY25 (Management Discussion & Analysis, excerpt)\n\nBusiness overview\nAranya Digital Services is an India-headquartered IT and ITeS company providing application\ndevelopment, cloud & infrastructure, data & AI, and digital engineering services. FY25 consolidated\nrevenue was \u20b918,400 Cr (FY24: \u20b916,900 Cr), up 8.9% YoY, with EBIT margin of 17.2% (FY24: 18.4%).\n\nRevenue mix (FY25)\n- By segment: BFSI 42%, Retail & CPG 22%, Healthcare & Life Sciences 17%, Digit",
