      "text_preview": "Aranya Digital Services Ltd \u2014 FY26 Cost Optimisation Mandate (CFO memo)\n\nTo: Delivery, Infrastructure, Procurement and Corporate leadership\nFrom: Group CFO\nRe: FY26 OpEx discipline and margin recovery\n\nContext\nFY25 EBIT margin fell to 17.2%. The Board has approved a margin-recovery target of +150 bps for FY26.\nWe expect roughly half from utilisation/pyramid actions (people) and half from third-party cost-out.\n\nTargets and guardrails\n- Third-party (non-people) OpEx reduction target: 6\u20139% of addre",
