      "text_preview": "Aranya Digital Services Ltd \u2014 Procurement & Spend Control Policy (extract)\n\n1) Competitive bidding\n- Three competitive bids mandatory for any commitment above \u20b91 Cr (USD ~120,000 equivalent).\n- Single-source above \u20b91 Cr requires CPO + category-head written justification.\n\n2) Purchase orders\n- No PO, no pay: all third-party spend above \u20b92 Lakh must be on an approved PO.\n- Off-PO / emergency spend permitted for production incidents but must be regularised within 30 days.\n- Known off-PO leakage: cl",
